  "instructions": [
    "Heat a kazan cauldron over medium heat and melt butter with olive oil.",
    "Add diced fennel and sauté until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in rice, ensuring each grain coats with oil and toast for 2 minutes.",
    "Pour in one cup of broth, bring to a gentle simmer, and cook until liquid is absorbed.",
    "Continue adding remaining broth in 1/2 cup portions, stirring frequently, until rice is al dente and creamy, about 18 minutes total.",
    "Remove from heat and stir in lactose-free cream, cheese, and lemon juice until fully incorporated.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste, and let the risotto rest for 2 minutes to thicken.",
    "Serve hot, optionally garnished with chopped fresh dill."
